1
00:00:01,140 --> 00:00:03,880
(Episode 70)

2
00:00:05,410 --> 00:00:06,410
Thank you.

3
00:00:07,010 --> 00:00:11,280
If it weren't for you, Baek Ho,
I never could've cornered Chae Hwa Young.

4
00:00:12,680 --> 00:00:13,920
You should get some rest now.

5
00:00:14,720 --> 00:00:16,790
You've been fighting
all on your own for so long.

6
00:00:17,790 --> 00:00:21,390
Even Chae Hwa Young won't find it easy
to get away without apologizing this time.

7
00:00:22,060 --> 00:00:25,160
Honestly, I just want
to get this revenge over with...

8
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:27,300
and go back to my mom.

9
00:00:28,070 --> 00:00:29,070
Well, for now...

10
00:00:30,070 --> 00:00:31,370
how about resting in my arms?

11
00:00:32,170 --> 00:00:34,840
What was that? Gosh, so cheesy!

12
00:01:32,930 --> 00:01:34,570
What the?

13
00:01:35,370 --> 00:01:37,340
Wait, what's Ma Seo Rin doing here?

14
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,670
(Name: Oh Jang Mi)

15
00:01:42,670 --> 00:01:44,380
Seriously, what's going on?

16
00:01:45,910 --> 00:01:49,580
Oh Jang Mi looks exactly like Ma Seo Rin.

17
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,720
What, they're twins?

18
00:01:58,890 --> 00:02:01,490
Wait, is she really unconscious?

19
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:06,600
What if this is Ma Seo Rin,
putting on an act to fool me?

20
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,300
No, that can't be it.

21
00:02:10,770 --> 00:02:14,170
The Ma Seo Rin at my house
doesn't have that scar.

22
00:02:16,070 --> 00:02:17,080
Darn it.

23
00:02:17,710 --> 00:02:19,680
Then what the heck is going on?

24
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:23,880
Your hand!

25
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,660
I feel great.

26
00:02:31,990 --> 00:02:33,190
The weather's amazing.

27
00:02:35,230 --> 00:02:36,260
And my girl is beautiful!

28
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:41,270
I love Oh Jang Mi!

29
00:02:43,900 --> 00:02:45,240
Hey, what's gotten into you today?

30
00:02:49,270 --> 00:02:50,540
Goodness.

31
00:02:58,620 --> 00:03:01,250
Honey, you should be resting at home.

32
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:05,260
But Hwa Young caused all this trouble,
and you're stressing out unnecessarily.

33
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:07,060
I'll be back.

34
00:03:07,630 --> 00:03:11,200
Okay. Try not to get stressed.
Think about your blood pressure.

35
00:03:11,830 --> 00:03:13,870
That Hwa Young, instead of being any help,

36
00:03:13,930 --> 00:03:16,530
she just causes you so much grief.
What are we going to do with her?

37
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:21,110
- You should just fire her while you can.
- Will you be quiet?

38
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:24,340
Firing CEO Chae isn't that simple.

39
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:33,950
(Director Kang Jun Ho)

40
00:03:35,650 --> 00:03:38,060
She must have seen my missed call.

41
00:03:38,790 --> 00:03:40,890
The woman who claims she's my mother
isn't calling me back.

42
00:03:41,730 --> 00:03:43,160
After going to all the trouble
of finding me,

43
00:03:43,730 --> 00:03:46,130
why is she refusing to see me now?

44
00:03:46,930 --> 00:03:50,200
What does she even look like?
What has her life been like?

45
00:03:50,740 --> 00:03:53,840
Just why? Why did you abandon me?

46
00:03:54,410 --> 00:03:55,410
Why?

47
00:04:01,110 --> 00:04:03,650
I thought you took the afternoon off.

48
00:04:04,620 --> 00:04:05,620
Yes.

49
00:04:05,780 --> 00:04:09,090
The CEO is giving her apology interview.
The Chairman will be there. You should go.

50
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:10,590
Understood.

51
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,060
CEO Chae.

52
00:04:18,430 --> 00:04:21,670
All eyes have been on you recently
due to several controversies.

53
00:04:22,470 --> 00:04:24,970
Could you tell us
what's been going through your mind?

54
00:04:25,870 --> 00:04:27,340
My heart has been heavy.

55
00:04:28,410 --> 00:04:32,840
In leading Dream Hotel,
my constant pursuit of perfection...

56
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:37,550
perhaps I lost sight of
what was truly in people's hearts.

57
00:04:38,650 --> 00:04:41,020
I am deeply remorseful.

58
00:04:41,350 --> 00:04:45,660
- As for the power abuse controversy.
- There's no excuse. I was in the wrong.

59
00:04:47,530 --> 00:04:48,530
The truth is, on that day,

60
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:53,030
I had just undergone extensive tests
at the hospital.

61
00:04:53,030 --> 00:04:55,170
- Extensive test?
- Right.

62
00:04:56,370 --> 00:04:59,570
I was in an extremely
unstable emotional state.

63
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,970
I know that's not an excuse,

64
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:05,380
but I'm only human.

65
00:05:05,980 --> 00:05:08,510
Don't I have moments
where I just break down?

66
00:05:08,650 --> 00:05:10,480
When you say extensive tests,
what kind of...

67
00:05:13,350 --> 00:05:15,220
Hello there.
Thank you all for your hard work.

68
00:05:17,090 --> 00:05:19,720
- Reporter Kim.
- Yes?

69
00:05:19,990 --> 00:05:22,330
This is the doctor's official opinion.

70
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:26,700
It says they suspect my daughter-in-law
has a tumor in her colon.

71
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:27,830
I see.

72
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:31,300
There's no need to write
about this in your articles.

73
00:05:31,870 --> 00:05:33,340
It's a private matter, after all.

74
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,870
Yes, of course.
It's her private medical information.

75
00:05:36,370 --> 00:05:38,040
The day that video was taken,

76
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:41,350
I had just received
my test results from the hospital.

77
00:05:41,980 --> 00:05:43,650
The news was devastating.

78
00:05:45,050 --> 00:05:47,390
And that's why, I was a bit sensitive...

79
00:05:47,990 --> 00:05:50,120
with that employee in the parking lot.

80
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:54,060
Of course,
there's no excuse for my behavior.

81
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:57,200
I am truly, deeply sorry.

82
00:05:57,830 --> 00:06:02,530
My daughter-in-law is not
normally like that at all.

83
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:05,140
- You understand, don't you, Reporter Kim?
- Of course.

84
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:06,870
It's heartbreaking to hear.

85
00:06:08,370 --> 00:06:11,240
Gosh, all this gossip...

86
00:06:11,310 --> 00:06:14,410
It's affecting Dream's stock price.

87
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:18,020
What you write, Reporter Kim,
will determine if the stock plummets...

88
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:20,150
or skyrockets.

89
00:06:20,420 --> 00:06:24,220
- We're counting on you.
- Yes, of course, absolutely, Chairman.

90
00:06:33,930 --> 00:06:37,240
CEO Chae is probably recording
her apology video as we speak.

91
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:39,700
Man, I wish I could've seen
that glorious moment.

92
00:06:40,070 --> 00:06:42,810
I'm sure she's just making excuses
and lying through her teeth.

93
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:44,310
That's her to a T.

94
00:06:44,810 --> 00:06:46,210
I guess watching it
would've made my blood boil.

95
00:06:47,010 --> 00:06:48,850
Let's just get back to work.

96
00:06:50,050 --> 00:06:52,720
Still, there's one thing I can't get over.

97
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:57,360
- Regret what?
- The mechanic that we let get away.

98
00:06:57,890 --> 00:06:59,860
For all we know, that dashcam footage...

99
00:07:00,060 --> 00:07:03,160
could have contained the crucial evidence
about your father's accident.

100
00:07:03,290 --> 00:07:05,700
You're right.
Even though we didn't see it,

101
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:09,370
it could've been footage of
Chae Hwa Young harming your dad.

102
00:07:09,670 --> 00:07:10,700
Even now,

103
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:14,210
shouldn't we try to find out
where they took the mechanic?

104
00:07:14,710 --> 00:07:18,110
If we tail Manager Lee,
we'll probably be able to find him.

105
00:07:34,060 --> 00:07:35,390
That woman, my mother.

106
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:37,830
Is she really not going to call me?

107
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:42,500
I must meet you to see who you are. No!

108
00:07:43,730 --> 00:07:46,940
I have to hear the reason
you abandoned me.

109
00:07:50,980 --> 00:07:53,340
I'm sorry for worrying you, Father.

110
00:07:53,610 --> 00:07:56,780
I didn't side with you because I like you.

111
00:07:57,250 --> 00:08:00,180
I let this slide just this once
for the sake of Dream.

112
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:02,120
Yes, I am aware.

113
00:08:03,050 --> 00:08:04,890
I promise it won't happen again.

114
00:08:07,890 --> 00:08:10,060
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

115
00:08:10,330 --> 00:08:11,500
Looks like you're getting a call.

116
00:08:12,060 --> 00:08:13,060
Go on, answer it.

117
00:08:23,770 --> 00:08:25,040
This is Kang Nam Bong.

118
00:08:25,340 --> 00:08:29,150
- Yes.
- There's something I need to confirm.

119
00:08:29,350 --> 00:08:30,350
What is it about?

120
00:08:30,980 --> 00:08:33,520
- If it's not urgent...
- It's about Mr. Oh Bok Gil's accident.

121
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:36,820
There's something
I absolutely must confirm.

122
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,560
I see.

123
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,790
Then come to my office now.

124
00:08:43,460 --> 00:08:44,660
All right, I'm on my way.

125
00:08:51,300 --> 00:08:52,300
Oh, honey.

126
00:08:52,900 --> 00:08:54,640
Where are you going?

127
00:08:55,010 --> 00:08:59,810
- Something just came up.
- At this hour? What is it?

128
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:01,950
What's the point?
You wouldn't understand anyway.

129
00:09:02,010 --> 00:09:04,220
Do I have to report
every little detail to you?

130
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,280
Honey!

131
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:07,690
You know you've been acting
really strange lately, right?

132
00:09:08,290 --> 00:09:11,860
You fly off the handle over nothing
and put me down.

133
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:14,760
What in the world is wrong with you?
Are you...

134
00:09:15,330 --> 00:09:16,390
seeing someone else?

135
00:09:17,630 --> 00:09:18,630
What?

136
00:09:19,860 --> 00:09:21,670
From what I hear from my clients,

137
00:09:22,470 --> 00:09:24,300
when a husband is cheating,

138
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:28,470
they say the husbands always get annoyed
and snap at their wives over nothing.

139
00:09:28,810 --> 00:09:32,910
Do you realize you're acting exactly
like those cheating husbands right now?

140
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:34,780
What do you take me for?

141
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:39,350
Gosh, that's ridiculous. I don't have time
for this. I'll be back.

142
00:09:44,060 --> 00:09:45,090
Seriously?

143
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:48,960
Something's definitely off.

144
00:09:50,060 --> 00:09:51,730
Surely not,

145
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:57,470
but I'm a seasoned divorce lawyer.

146
00:09:57,800 --> 00:09:59,670
And I can't stand anything suspicious.

147
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,080
Kang Hyuk.

148
00:10:12,580 --> 00:10:15,150
You were right. I think Professor Kang
has caught on to something.

149
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:17,590
- What should I do?
- What did he say?

150
00:10:17,690 --> 00:10:20,390
He said he's on his way here now,
probably to confront me.

151
00:10:25,930 --> 00:10:28,370
- Oh, you're here.
- Yes.

152
00:10:42,380 --> 00:10:44,420
Gosh, this stupid occupational hazard.

153
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,680
Of all the people to suspect.

154
00:10:47,490 --> 00:10:50,490
To think I suspected my own husband,
who only has eyes for me.

155
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:55,530
You've really got a bad case
of professional paranoia, Han Young Ja.

156
00:10:56,690 --> 00:10:58,060
Shame on you, Han Young Ja.

157
00:11:08,270 --> 00:11:10,880
I was filming an apology video earlier,

158
00:11:11,210 --> 00:11:14,280
and I was so exhausted I got a bit snippy.
I'm sorry, Professor.

159
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:18,720
But seeing you now
is actually giving me strength.

160
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:23,690
CEO Chae is the one
who hurt Jang Mi's father.

161
00:11:24,490 --> 00:11:26,220
Right here,
in this hotel's parking garage.

162
00:11:27,690 --> 00:11:29,530
And to cover up her crime,

163
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:32,200
she put Jang Mi's unconscious father
in her car,

164
00:11:33,060 --> 00:11:35,130
and abandoned him on the road
where the accident supposedly happened.

165
00:11:36,030 --> 00:11:37,500
And then, she must have called you.

166
00:11:41,410 --> 00:11:42,410
Hwa Young.

167
00:11:43,610 --> 00:11:44,980
Hwa Young, about that day,

168
00:11:46,210 --> 00:11:47,650
when you called me out,

169
00:11:49,210 --> 00:11:51,980
did you have some other motive?

170
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:54,820
What day are you talking about?

171
00:11:55,050 --> 00:11:57,350
I'm talking about
Oh Bok Gil's car accident.

172
00:11:58,390 --> 00:11:59,890
According to Baek Ho,

173
00:12:00,660 --> 00:12:04,030
he seems to think that
you're just using me.

174
00:12:05,130 --> 00:12:08,600
And I'm very confused.

175
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:12,070
Using you? Who? Me?

176
00:12:13,070 --> 00:12:15,510
You think I would dare use you, Professor?

177
00:12:16,940 --> 00:12:19,280
I just want to know the truth.

178
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:23,580
You're the one who hit Oh Bok Gil
with your car, Professor.

179
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:26,620
What other truth could there be?

180
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:30,490
Why on earth would I use you?

181
00:12:31,290 --> 00:12:33,560
I have absolutely no idea
what you're talking about.

182
00:12:34,630 --> 00:12:35,930
Really?

183
00:12:36,660 --> 00:12:39,060
Hwa Young, you didn't have
any other motive...

184
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:42,670
when you called me out here, did you?

185
00:12:42,930 --> 00:12:45,070
Of course not. Absolutely not.

186
00:12:46,170 --> 00:12:47,670
I'm in love with you, Professor.

187
00:12:48,870 --> 00:12:50,810
I don't know what kind of
ulterior motive you mean,

188
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:54,810
but why would I ever do anything
to hurt the man I love?

189
00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:58,120
Nam Bong, how can you be
so clueless about my feelings?

190
00:13:01,220 --> 00:13:02,450
Nam Bong.

191
00:13:03,020 --> 00:13:05,390
You see me as some manipulative woman
with ulterior motives,

192
00:13:06,590 --> 00:13:09,260
and you came all the way here
at this hour to accuse me?

193
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:13,500
Gosh, if that's really what you think,
I'm so hurt.

194
00:13:14,530 --> 00:13:18,540
- No, that's not it...
- If I've done anything wrong,

195
00:13:21,470 --> 00:13:23,370
my only crime is loving you.

196
00:13:23,870 --> 00:13:26,980
- Hwa Young, wait.
- Even though I love you, Professor,

197
00:13:27,950 --> 00:13:30,750
I was the one who said we should break up,
purely for the children's sake.

198
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:33,750
How can you be so oblivious
to my feelings?

199
00:13:35,020 --> 00:13:37,150
I mean...

200
00:13:37,890 --> 00:13:39,520
I'm so sorry, Hwa Young.

201
00:13:39,590 --> 00:13:42,490
I swear, I wasn't suspecting you,
it's just that...

202
00:13:43,890 --> 00:13:47,330
Right. It was just such a coincidence,

203
00:13:47,700 --> 00:13:49,400
I was just curious, that's all.

204
00:13:52,170 --> 00:13:55,370
Of course I know how you feel, Hwa Young.

205
00:13:55,940 --> 00:13:57,440
Please, don't cry, Hwa Young.

206
00:13:58,180 --> 00:13:59,280
I'm sorry, okay?

207
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:01,310
I'm sorry.

208
00:14:08,390 --> 00:14:09,390
Mom!

209
00:14:10,090 --> 00:14:11,960
Mom!

210
00:14:15,060 --> 00:14:16,060
Oh, my.

211
00:14:17,060 --> 00:14:18,160
I'm home.

212
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:30,640
Oh, for goodness' sake!

213
00:14:31,010 --> 00:14:35,250
- Goodness! What's all this fuss about?
- Mom.

214
00:14:35,550 --> 00:14:37,950
This is earth-shattering.

215
00:14:39,220 --> 00:14:42,350
What is it? Tell me already!

216
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,570
Who is he to suspect me?

217
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:02,910
Twins?

218
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:16,250
Gosh, I couldn't hear what they said.

219
00:15:16,790 --> 00:15:18,520
Of all the times
for Chae Hwa Young to show up.

220
00:15:19,490 --> 00:15:21,260
What is Hong Ju trying to say?

221
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:24,300
Are you sure they're twins?

222
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:27,870
Mom, I'm telling you
I saw it with my own two eyes.

223
00:15:27,970 --> 00:15:32,570
That's ridiculous.
How can there be two Seo Rins?

224
00:15:32,940 --> 00:15:34,870
If they're twins, does that mean
Chae Hwa Young...

225
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:37,910
gave birth to both
Oh Jang Mi and Ma Seo Rin?

226
00:15:38,410 --> 00:15:39,640
I don't know about that,

227
00:15:39,940 --> 00:15:43,450
but I saw Oh Jang Mi in her hospital room.
She has a scar on one cheek...

228
00:15:43,510 --> 00:15:46,880
but her face is identical to Ma Seo Rin's.

229
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:51,290
- I was so shocked, I couldn't breathe.
- Oh my gosh, are you serious?

230
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:55,060
I thought it was Ma Seo Rin in the bed.
How many times must I tell you it's true?

231
00:15:55,060 --> 00:15:57,730
Well, it's just hard to believe.

232
00:15:57,800 --> 00:16:00,430
Then go and see for yourself, Mom.

233
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:02,900
See if I was seeing things
or if they're really twins.

234
00:16:03,300 --> 00:16:06,870
Fine. I'll go to the hospital
and see myself first thing tomorrow.

235
00:16:07,300 --> 00:16:08,970
Then I'll know for sure
if they're twins or not.

236
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:10,870
What do I do?

237
00:16:11,180 --> 00:16:14,210
If they go to Oh Jang Mi's room to check,
I'm in big trouble.

238
00:16:15,010 --> 00:16:17,610
It's only a matter of time
before they find out they're twins.

239
00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:40,140
- Manager Lee, we have a huge problem.
- What is it?

240
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:42,540
It looks like Yeom San Wol and Jin Hong Ju
saw Oh Jang Mi.

241
00:16:42,810 --> 00:16:44,910
No, wait. It seems
they haven't seen her yet,

242
00:16:45,610 --> 00:16:49,450
but they're highly suspicious
and plan to check her room tomorrow.

243
00:16:49,650 --> 00:16:52,950
- What? Her hospital room?
- That's right.

244
00:16:53,520 --> 00:16:56,220
Then it's only a matter of time
before everyone finds out they're twins.

245
00:16:56,920 --> 00:16:59,860
If that happens,
Father will find out immediately.

246
00:17:00,860 --> 00:17:02,160
What on earth am I going to do?

247
00:17:02,460 --> 00:17:03,560
This is serious.

248
00:17:04,060 --> 00:17:07,600
First thing tomorrow morning,
we need to get rid of Oh Jang Mi.

249
00:17:08,070 --> 00:17:10,070
She should've been taken care of
a long time ago.

250
00:17:10,370 --> 00:17:12,140
We've let her live for far too long.

251
00:17:13,570 --> 00:17:15,710
Oh Jang Mi.

252
00:17:16,670 --> 00:17:18,610
Deal with her at first light tomorrow.

253
00:17:32,260 --> 00:17:37,190
Tae Pyung, please, pick up.
There's no time. They might kill Seo Rin.

254
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:43,830
The person you are calling is unavailable.
Connecting to voicemail.

255
00:17:45,540 --> 00:17:46,600
What do I do?

256
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:50,570
Oh my, Seo Rin.
Seo Rin's life is in danger.

257
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:56,210
It's bad enough that
she's lying in a coma because of me,

258
00:17:57,050 --> 00:18:00,380
and now she's about to be killed
by the woman who raised her.

259
00:18:00,820 --> 00:18:03,290
No. No, Seo Rin.

260
00:18:03,920 --> 00:18:05,660
I will save you. I swear.

261
00:18:06,790 --> 00:18:08,030
I can't lose you like this.

262
00:18:25,140 --> 00:18:26,740
Yes? What's wrong, Jang Mi?

263
00:18:28,250 --> 00:18:31,150
It's about Seo Rin.
I think they're going to hurt her.

264
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:32,620
What?

265
00:18:33,350 --> 00:18:36,250
We have to move Seo Rin somewhere else
first thing in the morning.

266
00:18:36,590 --> 00:18:38,990
We have to get to her
before Chae Hwa Young does.

267
00:18:40,060 --> 00:18:42,060
Tae Pyung must be asleep.
He's not answering his phone...

268
00:18:42,490 --> 00:18:43,560
so I had no other choice.

269
00:18:44,030 --> 00:18:45,430
You did the right thing calling, Jang Mi.

270
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:48,800
Tomorrow morning, I'll start looking
for another hospital we can move her to.

271
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:54,140
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

272
00:18:57,310 --> 00:18:58,310
Hey...

273
00:18:58,980 --> 00:19:01,450
Baek Ho! You're here. Come and eat.

274
00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:04,550
- Baek Ho is here. Good.
- Hi, Uncle Baek Ho.

275
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:05,820
Hey, hi.

276
00:19:06,380 --> 00:19:07,620
Tae Pyung, get up. Now.

277
00:19:07,890 --> 00:19:09,950
- What?
- I'll explain as we go. Let's hurry.

278
00:19:10,290 --> 00:19:11,320
What's wrong?

279
00:19:12,020 --> 00:19:13,760
Did something happen to Jang Mi?

280
00:19:14,020 --> 00:19:16,160
- Is she in critical condition?
- No, that's not it.

281
00:19:16,630 --> 00:19:18,960
I called a private ambulance.
We're moving her to a different hospital.

282
00:19:19,060 --> 00:19:20,200
Tok Hee's hurt.

283
00:19:21,060 --> 00:19:23,030
Tok Hee can't die.

284
00:19:23,770 --> 00:19:26,640
Hey, I haven't even eaten yet.
Is this really that urgent?

285
00:19:26,700 --> 00:19:28,210
You're her legal guardian,
so we have to go now.

286
00:19:28,740 --> 00:19:30,910
Ma'am, Tok Hee will be fine.
Please don't worry.

287
00:19:31,410 --> 00:19:32,940
It's really nothing to worry about.
Everything's fine.

288
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:47,590
Father.

289
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:50,760
To make up for what happened,

290
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:54,200
I got you tickets to an opera you love.

291
00:19:54,870 --> 00:19:57,270
I was hoping you and Mrs. Yeom
could go today.

292
00:19:57,670 --> 00:19:59,570
- Really?
- An opera?

293
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:07,180
But I'm busy today.
Do we really have to go today?

294
00:20:07,340 --> 00:20:09,650
It's for the three o'clock show.
That works for you, doesn't it, Father?

295
00:20:10,350 --> 00:20:12,820
Team Leader Jin, we're having the meeting
at one o'clock today,

296
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:14,720
so come in early and get everything ready.

297
00:20:15,550 --> 00:20:19,160
- What?
- Chae Hwa Young wants to remove Seo Rin,

298
00:20:19,290 --> 00:20:23,360
and she's buying time to do it.
Grandfather, we have plans, remember?

299
00:20:24,060 --> 00:20:27,700
I called dibs on Grandfather.
You can just go to the opera another time.

300
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:28,830
Actually,

301
00:20:29,630 --> 00:20:34,400
I'm afraid I can't join you either.
I'm golfing with Chairman Lee today.

302
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:37,740
Then Mrs. Yeom can just join you for golf.

303
00:20:38,510 --> 00:20:41,510
San Wol, make sure you take good care
of Father, all right?

304
00:20:42,150 --> 00:20:43,150
Okay.

305
00:20:59,360 --> 00:21:01,400
- Did you look into it?
- I called them,

306
00:21:01,700 --> 00:21:04,330
and according to the nurse,
she still hasn't regained consciousness.

307
00:21:04,700 --> 00:21:07,870
Who knows?
She could be awake and just faking it.

308
00:21:08,710 --> 00:21:10,340
But that's not the problem right now.

309
00:21:10,770 --> 00:21:12,440
We need to get Oh Jang Mi
out of there, fast.

310
00:21:13,110 --> 00:21:14,750
Dealing with her comes after.

311
00:21:15,050 --> 00:21:18,820
Right, I've arranged
a short visit for you.

312
00:21:19,020 --> 00:21:21,080
Good. Is the car waiting?

313
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:22,720
I'm leaving now.

314
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,730
I have to get there
before Chae Hwa Young does.

315
00:21:30,260 --> 00:21:31,960
If I'm a step behind,
Seo Rin will be in danger.

316
00:21:35,430 --> 00:21:36,570
Here you go.

317
00:21:37,270 --> 00:21:38,700
Honey, eat up.

318
00:21:40,800 --> 00:21:43,070
Wow, what's the special occasion?

319
00:21:44,140 --> 00:21:45,510
What occasion?

320
00:21:45,940 --> 00:21:50,180
Just because I adore you.
I thought I'd show off my limited skills.

321
00:21:51,150 --> 00:21:52,150
By the way,

322
00:21:52,420 --> 00:21:56,150
- Baek Ho isn't up yet?
- He left at dawn for some reason.

323
00:21:56,650 --> 00:21:59,390
- He didn't even stop to eat.
- Could it be that...

324
00:21:59,790 --> 00:22:01,960
he went to see Director Ma?

325
00:22:03,330 --> 00:22:06,430
(Korea University Hospital)

326
00:22:13,970 --> 00:22:15,540
Hello,
I need the doctor's written opinion.

327
00:22:15,840 --> 00:22:16,910
I need it now.

328
00:22:18,010 --> 00:22:19,010
Jang Mi.

329
00:22:20,240 --> 00:22:22,110
The private transport is here.

330
00:22:22,510 --> 00:22:24,410
You can't let CEO Chae see you.

331
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:26,920
Stay here and keep a lookout.
Don't let anyone see you, no matter what.

332
00:22:27,150 --> 00:22:29,390
Okay. Please take good care of my sister.

333
00:22:42,830 --> 00:22:45,840
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

334
00:22:48,210 --> 00:22:50,040
I'm sure she had her reasons,

335
00:22:50,410 --> 00:22:53,580
but the love of a mother searching
for her son was genuine.

336
00:22:54,310 --> 00:22:55,450
Genuine?

337
00:22:56,180 --> 00:22:58,750
What kind of reason could possibly
keep her from meeting me?

338
00:22:59,550 --> 00:23:00,650
Did she remarry or something?

339
00:23:01,220 --> 00:23:04,090
Of course. She's married and happy by now,
having forgotten all about me.

340
00:23:04,690 --> 00:23:05,720
But still...

341
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:08,020
she can't even spare a moment to see me?

342
00:23:09,460 --> 00:23:10,790
I need to find out for myself.

343
00:23:17,130 --> 00:23:19,440
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

344
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:37,990
Oh no, what do I do?

345
00:23:39,060 --> 00:23:40,220
Chae Hwa Young's here.

346
00:23:40,760 --> 00:23:43,430
I hope Seo Rin is transferred safely.

347
00:23:56,740 --> 00:23:57,970
Got it, Ssangkal.

348
00:23:58,580 --> 00:23:59,910
You have your guys in position
over there, right?

349
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:02,580
Have them disguise themselves
as doctors to get close.

350
00:24:03,980 --> 00:24:06,150
We need to grab Oh Jang Mi
and get rid of her, no matter what.

351
00:24:06,980 --> 00:24:08,450
Let's not screw it up this time.

352
00:24:11,420 --> 00:24:14,290
- Please wait here.
- No, I'm going in myself.

353
00:24:15,060 --> 00:24:17,490
If you want it done right,
I have to do it myself.

354
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:22,230
(Korea University Hospital)

355
00:24:29,370 --> 00:24:32,680
- The person you are calling is...
- Right.

356
00:24:32,740 --> 00:24:35,880
I don't want to waste my energy
on a woman like you anymore.

357
00:24:38,950 --> 00:24:40,650
Let's meet at Han River Park at seven.

358
00:24:41,350 --> 00:24:42,620
If you don't show up today,

359
00:24:43,320 --> 00:24:44,350
I will never...

360
00:24:45,190 --> 00:24:46,260
ever...

361
00:24:46,820 --> 00:24:48,490
contact you or look for you again.

362
00:24:51,030 --> 00:24:52,300
This is the last time.

363
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:56,470
If you won't show up, even when I beg
just to see your face,

364
00:24:57,730 --> 00:24:59,670
I don't care if you're my mother or not.
Never again...

365
00:25:01,170 --> 00:25:03,010
waste another thought on you.

366
00:25:22,760 --> 00:25:24,830
I finally got the doctor
to sign the discharge papers.

367
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:26,160
Hurry and get going.

368
00:25:26,460 --> 00:25:27,830
- Let's move out.
- Right.

369
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:32,540
We're in big trouble.
CEO Chae is on her way.

370
00:25:32,840 --> 00:25:33,900
What?

371
00:26:11,780 --> 00:26:14,180
Mom, what are you doing here?
Weren't you golfing with the Chairman?

372
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:15,550
Do you really think
golf matters right now?

373
00:26:15,980 --> 00:26:19,980
Hong Ju, I think Hwa Young
has caught on to us, don't you?

374
00:26:21,280 --> 00:26:24,620
That must be why she pushed me
to go to the opera out of the blue.

375
00:26:24,820 --> 00:26:27,690
Since when was she so considerate of me,
giving me a ticket and all?

376
00:26:27,760 --> 00:26:30,190
- That's ridiculous.
- Really?

377
00:26:30,790 --> 00:26:33,930
Do you think CEO Chae
actually overheard us?

378
00:26:34,330 --> 00:26:37,400
Is she trying to sneak her away
so we can't prove she's Oh Jang Mi's twin?

379
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:38,600
That has to be it.

380
00:26:39,540 --> 00:26:41,040
We should've been one step ahead of her.

381
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:43,670
Where is it? Where?
Which room is the twin in?

382
00:26:43,770 --> 00:26:45,410
- Where's the elevator?
- There!

383
00:27:18,710 --> 00:27:19,710
It's here.

384
00:28:20,500 --> 00:28:22,010
(The First Man)

385
00:28:22,070 --> 00:28:25,640
If they're twins, why did they let
that woman raise Oh Jang Mi?

386
00:28:25,740 --> 00:28:28,280
What if CEO Chae is the one
who stole Ma Seo Rin?

387
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:31,210
Jun Ho is desperate to see me.

388
00:28:31,210 --> 00:28:32,720
He must be waiting so eagerly.

389
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:35,220
Then shall I take you to
Han River Park for seven?

390
00:28:35,420 --> 00:28:37,150
Something's not right with Chae Hwa Young.

391
00:28:37,520 --> 00:28:39,060
Who is this child?

392
00:28:39,660 --> 00:28:40,920
Could it be her son?

393
00:28:42,130 --> 00:28:44,130
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
